 ==============================================
 Bond energy with respect to atomic create runs
 ==============================================
  
 The bond energy printed here is computed as an energy difference between molecule and single atoms (create runs).
 These atoms are usually computed as SPHERICALLY SYMMETRIC, SPIN-RESTRICTED, and NEUTRAL.


